# BUFSIZE
#
#
# This file provides a means to set values for various system buffer sizes.
# Some system buffer size values available for change are:
#
#	ma		maximum argument (and environment) size
#	mn 		maximum name
#	mp 		maximum path
#	ml		maximum line
#	nn		node-name length
#	hn		host-name length
#	un		user-name length
#	ua		user-attr length
#	gn		group-name length
#	pn		project-name length
#	pw 		passwd entry
#	sp 		shadow entry
#	gr 		group entry
#	pj		project entry
#	pr 		network protocol entry
#	nm 		network mask entry
#	nw 		network network entry
#	ho 		network host entry
#	sv		network service entry
#	fs		file-system type length
#	zn		zone-name (fro Zone-Info) length
#
#


